AS3911

Modules

 AS3911 RFID Communication
 

This part of the AS9311 module abstracts Communication with an ISO14443-A or ISO14443-B card including features required for EMV.


 AS3911 Interrupt Handling
 

This part of the AS3911 module abstracts AS3911 interrupt handling.


 AS3911 SPI IO
 

This part of the AS3911 module provides access to the AS3911 via the SPI.

Define Documentation

#define AS3911_CMD_ADJUST_REGULATORS   0x16

Adjust the voltage regulators.

#define AS3911_CMD_CALIBRATE_ANTENNA   0x18

Calibrate antenna trimming.

#define AS3911_CMD_CALIBRATE_C_SENSOR   0x1D

Calibrate the capacitive sensor.

#define AS3911_CMD_CALIBRATE_MODULATION   0x17

Calibrate modulation depth.

#define AS3911_CMD_CLEAR_FIFO   0x02

Clear the FIFO and stop all activities (e.g. timers).

#define AS3911_CMD_CLEAR_SQUELCH   0x15

Clear squelch gain reduction and stop any ongoing squelch process.

#define AS3911_CMD_FUSE_PPROM   0x3E

Fuse poly fuses with data from the RAM.

#define AS3911_CMD_INITIAL_RF_COLLISION   0x08

Perform NFC initial RF collision avoidance.

#define AS3911_CMD_LOAD_PPROM   0x3D

Load data from the poly fuses to RAM.

#define AS3911_CMD_MASK_RECEIVE_DATA   0x10

Disable receiver, RSSI, and AGC.

#define AS3911_CMD_MEASURE_AMPLITUDE   0x13

Measure singal amplitude on RFI inputs.

#define AS3911_CMD_MEASURE_CAPACITANCE   0x1E

Measure the capacitance between CSI and CSO pins.

#define AS3911_CMD_MEASURE_PHASE   0x19

Measure the phase difference between the RFO and RFI signals.

#define AS3911_CMD_MEASURE_RSSI   0x1A

clear the RSSI bits and restart RSSI measurement.

#define AS3911_CMD_MEASURE_VSS   0x1F

Measure the power supply voltage.

#define AS3911_CMD_NORMAL_NFC_MODE   0x0B

Switch from NFC target bit rate detection mode to normal NFC mode.

#define AS3911_CMD_RESPONSE_RF_COLLISION_0   0x0A

Perform NFC response RF Collision avoidance with n=0.

#define AS3911_CMD_RESPONSE_RF_COLLISION_N   0x09

Perform NFC response RF collision avoidance.

#define AS3911_CMD_SET_DEFAULT   0x01

Put the chip into the default state (same as after power-up).

#define AS3911_CMD_SQUELCH   0x14

Start squelch process.

#define AS3911_CMD_START_GP_TIMER   0x20

Start the general purpose timer.

#define AS3911_CMD_START_MASK_RECEIVE_TIMER   0x22

Start the mask-receive timer.

#define AS3911_CMD_START_NO_RESPONSE_TIMER   0x23

Start the no-repsonse timer.

#define AS3911_CMD_START_WUP_TIMER   0x21

Start the wake-up timer.

#define AS3911_CMD_TEST_ACCESS   0x3C

Enable R/W access to the test registers.

#define AS3911_CMD_TRANSMIT_REQA   0x06

Transmit REQA.

#define AS3911_CMD_TRANSMIT_WITH_CRC   0x04

Transmit with CRC.

#define AS3911_CMD_TRANSMIT_WITHOUT_CRC   0x05

Transmit without CRC.

#define AS3911_CMD_TRANSMIT_WUPA   0x07

Transmit WUPA.

#define AS3911_CMD_TRANSPARENT_MODE   0x1C

Set the chip into transparent mode.

#define AS3911_CMD_UNMASK_RECEIVE_DATA   0x11

Enable receiver, RSSI, and AGC.

#define AS3911_COLLISION_ERROR   -2

Bit collision error.

#define AS3911_CRC_ERROR   -3

CRC incorrect.

#define AS3911_FIFO_RECEIVE_WL0   64

AS3911 water level interrupt receive water level if IO configuration register 1 bit fifo_lr is zero.

#define AS3911_FIFO_RECEIVE_WL1   80

AS3911 water level interrupt receive water level if IO configuration register 1 bit fifo_lr is one.

#define AS3911_FIFO_SIZE   96

AS3911 FIFO size (bytes).

#define AS3911_FIFO_TRANSMIT_WL0   32

AS3911 water level interrupt transmit water level if IO configuration register 1 bit fifo_lt is zero.

#define AS3911_FIFO_TRANSMIT_WL1   16

AS3911 water level interrupt transmit water level if IO configuration register 1 bit fifo_lt is one.
